OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunday will bring a mix of
OL,6,Fsunshine and blustery showers, the
OL,7,Fshowers locally heavy with hail and
OL,8,Fthunder. Remaining windy, particularly
OL,9,Fin the northwest with coastal gales.
OL,10,FFeeling rather cool overall.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMany areas will become dry
OL,13,Fwith clear spells developing fairly
OL,14,Fwidely. Winds easing allowing a patchy
OL,15,Frural frost in some prone spots.
OL,16,FHowever showers will linger across
OL,17,Fnorthern Scotland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
