OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA dry start for many, with
OL,6,Fshowers initially in the northwest and
OL,7,Ffar southwest. Showers will soon
OL,8,Fdevelop widely, these will be locally
OL,9,Fheavy and carry a risk of thunder.
